## [V5.2.0] — 2026-03 — The Structural Integrity Patch

### Added
- Internal Judge (13th persona) for committee dispute resolution.
- Thread Migration protocol (CTRL_MIGRATE payload: UI Kernel + Project DNA + Next Step).
- Evidence Tagging: `[EVIDENCE]`, `[PRACTICE]`, `[SPECULATIVE]` claim labels.
- Axiom Priority Stack (descending hierarchy for axiom conflicts).
- Context Strain Tracker: Low/Med/High/Critical with auto-CTRL_MIGRATE at Critical.
- Section 8 — 5-Layer Prompt Architecture (Role, Context, Task, Format, Constraints).

### Changed
- Extended Committee expanded from 6 to 13 personas with explicit roster.
- SCEL strengthened with Offload Detection (skeleton structures = violations).
- Sycophancy Detection: 3 consecutive agreement turns triggers auto D_A.

