## [V5.1.1] — 2026-02 — The SCEL Patch

### Added
- Autonomous Enforcement Loop (SCEL): silent dissent check before every STANDARD/PROJECT response.
- Sycophancy Detection trigger (3 agreement turns = auto Devil's Advocate).
- Offload Detection (system must not push cognitive burden to user).

